{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2878420/extras/market_owner.gif?t=1737624440\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this cozy island town, you can order goods from the dock, buy stands from the lumberjack, place your goods, and make sales! Cultivate your own produce on your farm or in your greenhouse. Raise animals and use their products or meats, catch various fish with your boat, and produce more goods in your workshop. Hire employees to assist with daily tasks. Decorate and expand your market day by day. Look forward to fun seasonal and surprise events that will affect your sales and surroundings. Challenge other players across the world to see who the best merchant is. There is something for everyone, and more features are on the way!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Farming</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2878420/extras/farming.gif?t=1737624440\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Buy seeds or saplings, grow products, and sell them in your market. Expand your farm or greenhouse to cultivate every season.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Workshop</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2878420/extras/workshop.gif?t=1737624440\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cut meats, bake fresh items, or ferment drinks using the drink machine, with recipes available for each tool to help you get started.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Livestock</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2878420/extras/livestock.gif?t=1737624440\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Buy cows, goats, and chickens to raise in your barn. Feed them daily, and they will provide produce such as milk and eggs.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Fishing &amp; Sailing</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2878420/extras/fishing.gif?t=1737624440\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Acquire a boat, a paddle, and a fishing rod to catch both regular and special fish, then sell them at your market. You may even find sunken treasures while sailing!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Events &amp; Seasons</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2878420/extras/events_and_seasons.gif?t=1737624440\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Keep an eye on special events that occur throughout the year in different seasons. Events such as Halloween can significantly impact customer preferences, purchasing habits, and cause prices to fluctuate.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Employees</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2878420/extras/employee.gif?t=1737624440\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hire employees according to your needs and automate your store's processes. Be careful employees don\u2019t work for free! You can hire staff to help at the checkout, with cleaning, and with restocking your empty crates.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Grab your friends and start your journey in Old Market Simulator today! Don't forget to share your feedback in the discussions and feel free to join our Discord channel, where we listen to you to make the game more fun!</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Farmer's Joy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2878420/5fda7352a81cbbc4458cb7ddb92474c75df4b701.jpg"},{"name":"Tree-Mendous","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2878420/5fda7352a81cbbc4458cb7ddb92474c75df4b701.jpg"},{"name":"Fish Whisperer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2878420/5fd