://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2878420/extras/livestock.gif?t=1737624440\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Buy cows, goats, and chickens to raise in your barn. Feed them daily, and they will provide produce such as milk and eggs.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Fishing &amp; Sailing</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2878420/extras/fishing.gif?t=1737624440\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Acquire a boat, a paddle, and a fishing rod to catch both regular and special fish, then sell them at your market. You may even find sunken treasures while sailing!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Events &amp; Seasons</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2878420/extras/events_and_seasons.gif?t=1737624440\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Keep an eye on special events that occur throughout the year in different seasons. Events such as Halloween can significantly impact customer preferences, purchasing habits, and cause prices to fluctuate.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Employees</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2878420/extras/employee.gif?t=1737624440\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hire employees according to your needs and automate your store's processes. Be careful employees don\u2019t work for free! You can hire staff to help at the checkout, with cleaning, and with restocking your empty crates.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Grab your friends and start your journey in Old Market Simulator today! Don't forget to share your feedback in the discussions and feel free to join our Discord channel, where we listen to you to make the game more fun!</p>","developers":["Alcedo Games"],"genres":[{"description":"Simulation","id":"28"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.